Commentary Text: Avesh Khan to Saha, out Caught by (sub)Prerak Mankad!! Nice touch from Avesh Khan as he pats Saha on the shoulder for his knock. What an outstanding catch though to end a superb innings. Saha steps out and heaves the back of a length delivery in the air, it is going wide of deep square leg but Mankad - the sub - keeps his eyes on it and hangs on, does well to keep his balance and body inside the cushions as he was close to it, after completing the catch. Relief for LSG but Saha walks off to a deserved standing ovation. Saha c (sub)Prerak Mankad b Avesh Khan 81(43) [4s-10 6s-4]

Commentary Text: Mohit Sharma to Mayers, out Caught by Rashid Khan!! That's a magnificent catch by Rashid Khan! You can't keep him out of the game, can you? Was a slower short ball by Mohit Sharma and Mayers went for the hook. Gets a top edge towards deep square leg and Rashid Khan is quick to sprint across to his right as he completes an outstanding diving catch.
